M o r t i m e r  T w a n g   &  O r l i n g o

in one musicdisk..

B-Boy Culture, HipHop Music, Grafitty Spraying.

That's basicly the essence of this group..

HipHop is a way of live, once you understand that you can call yourself
HipHop..

Black Sista IS HipHop.. never forget that..

 enjoy the show.. Peace..


